1
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:29,900
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,780 --> 00:01:33,940
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:54,680
Fuling,

4
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,840
get me some alum,

5
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:56,960
clear water,

6
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,960
and filter cloth.

7
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:06,950
Your Highness.

8
00:02:09,289 --> 00:02:10,150
Your Highness.

9
00:02:10,450 --> 00:02:11,580
Excuse me, Miss Qin.

10
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,700
Someone robbed

11
00:02:12,930 --> 00:02:15,170
my coroner's kit just now.

12
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:17,480
I ran after him for a while,
but still lost him.

13
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:18,350
I was thinking about

14
00:02:18,350 --> 00:02:19,680
turning to constables.

15
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:23,500
Then I found the coroner's kit
right in front of the office.

16
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,889
Missing any autopsy tools?

17
00:02:24,889 --> 00:02:26,150
That's the weird part.

18
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:27,640
I checked carefully.

19
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,730
Nothing was lost.

20
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:30,520
What's more, the tools
are in the exact same place

21
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,200
as before.

22
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:34,610
Open it and let's see.

23
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,930
[Postmortem Report]

24
00:02:57,690 --> 00:02:58,620
Anything wrong?

25
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:04,079
Jinyu Bone-setting Ointment,

26
00:03:04,079 --> 00:03:05,760
a precious and priceless medicine

27
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,790
to heal bones and tendons,

28
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:08,190
only sold in the capital.

29
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:11,930
And you even know the medicine
only sold in the capital?

30
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,410
I'm a physician

31
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:16,780
curious about special medicines.

32
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:20,570
In this case,

33
00:03:21,010 --> 00:03:22,940
the thief not only has a bone injury

34
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:25,030
but also comes from a rich family.

35
00:03:25,690 --> 00:03:26,820
Is it a strong smell?

36
00:03:27,130 --> 00:03:27,640
Yes.

37
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:31,120
This person probably has nothing to do
with the wedding procession.

38
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,170
He didn't know
the previous autopsy results,

39
00:03:33,170 --> 00:03:35,360
so he held and checked
the report for quite a while,

40
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,290
leaving the smell of the ointment.

41
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:42,190
Your Highness, you can smell it.

42
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:55,850
I didn't see anything.

43
00:03:55,850 --> 00:03:56,920
I swear I didn't.

44
00:03:59,010 --> 00:04:00,470
Stand straight and speak.

45
00:04:02,850 --> 00:04:03,980
News from the capital.

46
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:05,460
Wei Qizhi, the Wei family's eldest
legitimate young master,

47
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,640
wasn't injured taming a horse,

48
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,040
but got his right leg
broken by Duke of Song

49
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,040
and was locked up at home.

50
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:11,450
So his half-brother, Wei Yanzhi,
sent the bride off instead of him.

51
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:12,760
The day after the wedding procession

52
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,320
left the capital,
Wei Qizhi escaped and has been

53
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,450
missing since then.

54
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,350
That day, the man who pushed the tower

55
00:04:24,350 --> 00:04:25,950
and hurt me seemed crippled.

56
00:04:26,010 --> 00:04:27,570
Would Duke of Song
badly injure the Wei family's

57
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:29,030
legitimate young master?

58
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,660
Unless Wei Qizhi
made a horrendous mistake.

59
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,320
If he was Song Rou's lover...

60
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:36,160
Song Rou would marry another nobleman.

61
00:04:36,690 --> 00:04:38,130
Love turned into hatred; he killed her

62
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:39,350
out of wrath. That makes sense.

63
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:41,250
But who was the one
playing ghost to scare me?

64
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:43,580
Wei Qizhi couldn't be
so light on his feet.

65
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,820
His leg injury may not be real.

66
00:04:45,930 --> 00:04:46,990
Only by finding him

67
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,590
can we figure out the truth.

68
00:04:48,590 --> 00:04:49,920
You can examine it here.

69
00:04:50,050 --> 00:04:51,450
I'll have Bai Feng protect you.

70
00:04:51,450 --> 00:04:52,840
I'm going to meet Wei Yanzhi

71
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:54,240
and see what he has to say.

72
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:07,970
Duke of Song not only

73
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,330
failed to discipline his daughter

74
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,800
but also asked his nephew

75
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:14,480
to destroy the body and evidence

76
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,810
to deceive His Majesty.

77
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:17,450
Your actions

78
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:21,520
have shown a complete disregard
for my Yue family,

79
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:23,050
for His Majesty,

80
00:05:23,810 --> 00:05:25,610
and for the national law!

81
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,500
Please calm down, Your Grace.

82
00:05:27,810 --> 00:05:28,720
I simply couldn't

83
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,160
bear to see Rou be accused

84
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,890
of infidelity after her death.

85
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:34,890
So I ordered Wei Cheng to burn the body

86
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,490
in case the postmortem report
to the Ministry of Justice

87
00:05:37,490 --> 00:05:40,760
would make both our families
a laughing stock in the capital.

88
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,490
I

89
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,610
will take all the blame.

90
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:46,590
Please spare the others
in the wedding procession.

91
00:05:46,590 --> 00:05:48,640
I made the decision to burn the body.

92
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:50,570
It has nothing to do
with Vice Commandant Wei.

93
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:51,250
Wei Cheng!

94
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,300
Song Rou's death

95
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:56,040
is closely related to the person
whom she had an affair with.

96
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,400
You were in such a hurry
to destroy the evidence.

97
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,490
Was it to cover up your family's stigma

98
00:06:00,490 --> 00:06:02,370
or to protect the adulterer?

99
00:06:03,130 --> 00:06:03,610
I just...

100
00:06:03,610 --> 00:06:06,080
Please stop covering
for the Eldest Young Master, my lord.

101
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,940
Your Highness,

102
00:06:07,010 --> 00:06:07,670
Your Grace,

103
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:10,130
the person who had an affair
with Lady Song Rou

104
00:06:10,130 --> 00:06:11,659
is our Eldest Young Master,

105
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:12,550
Wei Qizhi.

106
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:18,280
Is there any solid evidence?

107
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:21,200
The Eldest Young Master
admitted it himself.

108
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:23,080
Madam found that Lady Song was pregnant,

109
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:23,850
so Lady Song

110
00:06:24,050 --> 00:06:26,570
had no choice but to confess her affair
with the Eldest Young Master.

111
00:06:26,570 --> 00:06:27,690
Duke of Song

112
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:31,250
was so furious that he broke
Young Master Qizhi's leg.

113
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,400
Regardless of your motives,

114
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,530
you committed a severe crime of arson.

115
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,960
You're under arrest.

116
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,560
Take him away.

117
00:06:44,570 --> 00:06:45,200
Go.

118
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,280
Vice Commandant Wei,

119
00:06:49,370 --> 00:06:51,080
did Wei Cheng

120
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,159
tell the truth?

121
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:56,159
My brother

122
00:06:57,050 --> 00:06:59,710
had been on good terms
with Rou since childhood.

123
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,320
So I didn't overthink it.

124
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:04,159
Not until Duke of Song asked me
to send Rou off instead of my brother

125
00:07:04,159 --> 00:07:05,159
did I find out that

126
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,250
he and Rou

127
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:09,400
had made a terrible mistake.

128
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,570
You and Wei Qizhi lived
under the same roof.

129
00:07:11,570 --> 00:07:12,370
How come

130
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:14,630
you don't know his whereabouts?

131
00:07:14,890 --> 00:07:15,810
Two years ago,

132
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:20,130
I rode on Duke of Song's coat-tails
and joined the Patrol Battalion.

133
00:07:20,130 --> 00:07:21,990
My brother had a big fight with me,

134
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:24,250
and he's refused to talk to me since then.

135
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:25,800
So I really have no idea.

136
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,050
Why did you have a big fight?

137
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,840
Because

138
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:33,470
my father's legitimate wife
wanted my brother to marry Rou.

139
00:07:33,470 --> 00:07:35,250
But given the Wei family's
average background,

140
00:07:35,250 --> 00:07:37,110
Duke of Song didn't approve of it.

141
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,860
My brother's pride resulted in

142
00:07:39,130 --> 00:07:40,330
the growing distance

143
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:42,290
between him and the Duke of Song.

144
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,760
He didn't want me to accept
the Duke's help, I guess.

145
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,220
Is Wei Qizhi left-handed?

146
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:50,159
Yes,

147
00:07:50,810 --> 00:07:51,370
he is.

148
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:55,180
It's said that
being born left-handed is a jinx.

149
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,330
So his mother

150
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:59,730
forced him to use
his right hand since he was young.

151
00:08:00,050 --> 00:08:01,580
Few people know about this.

152
00:08:05,130 --> 00:08:06,659
Your Highness, I lied to you

153
00:08:06,930 --> 00:08:08,659
in order to protect my brother.

154
00:08:08,890 --> 00:08:09,460
I

155
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:11,130
shouldn't have done this.

156
00:08:11,130 --> 00:08:11,700
You...

157
00:08:12,010 --> 00:08:13,890
You almost screwed things up!

158
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,470
I

159
00:08:17,410 --> 00:08:18,740
have let you down, sirs.

160
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:20,170
Miss Song

161
00:08:21,010 --> 00:08:22,610
passed away in Jingzhou.

162
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,200
Before we catch the murderer,

163
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,260
you'll be grounded

164
00:08:26,570 --> 00:08:28,030
in the Eastern Courtyard.

165
00:08:46,780 --> 00:08:48,840
We've finally got to the bottom of it.

166
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,380
We still need to verify the truth.

167
00:08:54,090 --> 00:08:55,090
The priority now

168
00:08:55,730 --> 00:08:57,490
is to find Song Rou's head

169
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:00,150
and the murder weapon.

170
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,080
Fuling, silver chopsticks.

171
00:09:41,970 --> 00:09:42,630
My Lady,

172
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:45,140
the alum indeed removed all the residues.

173
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,650
It looks like some sort of

174
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:48,800
silk gauze.

175
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,440
Not gauze.

176
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,490
It's paper.

177
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,340
Wei Yanzhi confessed.

178
00:09:57,850 --> 00:09:58,710
What did he say?

179
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,030
He turned in his brother,

180
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:01,730
Wei Qizhi,

181
00:10:02,090 --> 00:10:03,490
who had long been in love with Song Rou.

182
00:10:03,490 --> 00:10:05,090
And he was born left-handed.

183
00:10:05,490 --> 00:10:06,680
Born left-handed?

184
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:08,280
Does he usually use his left hand?

185
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:10,210
Then many people should know that.

186
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:12,890
He was forced to use his right hand
since he was young.

187
00:10:12,890 --> 00:10:14,020
So few people know it

188
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:16,150
other than those really close to him.

189
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:19,220
I found this paper scrap
from Song Rou's stomach.

190
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,970
Song Rou had been living
a luxurious life since birth.

191
00:10:21,970 --> 00:10:23,610
Why would she swallow

192
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:24,670
such coarse paper?

193
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:27,410
How important
is the content written on it?

194
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,360
Maybe the key is not the content.

195
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,800
Sometimes, to protect

196
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,760
the source of information,
the spy in the army

197
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:35,130
will destroy
insignificant intelligence as well.

198
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:36,660
The source of information?

199
00:10:37,890 --> 00:10:39,110
Different types of paper

200
00:10:39,110 --> 00:10:40,910
can reveal the writers' habits.

201
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:42,820
Although the handwriting on this

202
00:10:42,820 --> 00:10:44,800
has been dissolved by gastric fluid,

203
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,760
this paper appears unusually durable,

204
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,850
not something
ordinary people can purchase.

205
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:50,890
My Lady, is that sparkling thing

206
00:10:50,890 --> 00:10:52,600
gold powder?

207
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,760
Not as bright as gold powder.

208
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,620
It's orpiment.

209
00:11:02,210 --> 00:11:04,370
Orpiment is often used
to make golden lacquer.

210
00:11:04,370 --> 00:11:07,010
Add raw golden lacquer
to wood pulp to produce

211
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:10,730
the dusted-gold paper,
also known as "mini scattered-gold paper."

212
00:11:10,730 --> 00:11:11,400
I know that!

213
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:12,730
I know the dusted-gold paper.

214
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:15,850
This kind of paper gives off
a faint lacquer tree scent.

215
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,890
And it's cheaper
than scattered-gold paper.

216
00:11:17,890 --> 00:11:19,760
Ordinary aristocrats who can't afford
scattered-gold paper

217
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,760
would write on dusted-gold paper instead.

218
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,490
According to the information
from the capital,

219
00:11:23,490 --> 00:11:24,850
the Wei family
may be an average household,

220
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:25,850
but Wei Qizhi

221
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:27,730
is pretty pretentious and willful.

222
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:28,730
He likes playing the zither,

223
00:11:28,730 --> 00:11:30,160
so he learnt
how to make the zither himself.

224
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,060
He likes horse riding,

225
00:11:31,060 --> 00:11:32,520
so he tried to tame the horse on his own.

226
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,610
He likes porcelain.

227
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:35,640
So porcelain items
are everywhere in his house.

228
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:36,400
In this case,

229
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:39,670
this dusted-gold paper
suits his temperament.

230
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,280
Right now, this paper scrap

231
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:43,810
is the only evidence
related to the murderer.

232
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:45,820
The Wei brothers grew up together.

233
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:47,800
I want to meet Wei Yanzhi
for confirmation.

234
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:49,040
It's said that Wei Yanzhi fell ill

235
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:50,890
with a high fever after he went back.

236
00:11:50,890 --> 00:11:52,620
The Yue family can't ignore it.

237
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:53,760
If you want to see him,

238
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,850
you'll have to spend

239
00:11:54,850 --> 00:11:56,180
some time treating him.

240
00:12:02,230 --> 00:12:02,750
Sir,

241
00:12:03,610 --> 00:12:04,610
two buns, please.

242
00:12:04,610 --> 00:12:05,150
Okay.

243
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,250
Two.

244
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,440
Thief! Catch him!

245
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,430
Stop there! Catch the thief!

246
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,390
Catch the thief!

247
00:12:18,850 --> 00:12:20,090
Where did he go?

248
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,560
Thief! Catch the thief!

249
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,120
You got this.

250
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:28,570
Okay.

251
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:50,660
Thief, you

252
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,330
wanted to steal the postmortem report?

253
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:55,660
Thanks to His Highness's brilliant idea,

254
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:58,020
we caught you, the key figure in the case.

255
00:12:58,370 --> 00:13:00,030
Will you surrender yourself,

256
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:02,040
or do you want us to take you by force?

257
00:13:04,330 --> 00:13:05,090
Young Master Qizhi,

258
00:13:05,090 --> 00:13:05,680
I...

259
00:13:15,610 --> 00:13:16,330
As if

260
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,680
I had a choice.

261
00:13:26,070 --> 00:13:27,000
Come in, please.

262
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:36,040
You have a high fever.

263
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,610
There's no need for courtesy.

264
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:39,070
Thank you, Your Highness.

265
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,810
You're seriously ill,

266
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,890
but why did you open the window?

267
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,520
I wanted

268
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:49,690
to get some fresh air.

269
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:52,210
You are taking a turn for the worse.

270
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:53,670
Is the medicine not right?

271
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,050
Any prescriptions?

272
00:13:57,250 --> 00:13:58,250
It's on the table.

273
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:06,490
Don't worry, Vice Commandant Wei.

274
00:14:06,490 --> 00:14:08,890
Miss Qin is a miracle-working physician
who cured the Grand Princess.

275
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:10,950
She came all the way here to treat you.

276
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:13,200
I dare not trouble you, Miss Qin.

277
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:15,280
Don't worry, Vice Commandant Wei.

278
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:17,680
It's a physician's duty to treat patients.

279
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:22,950
Vice Commandant Wei,

280
00:14:22,950 --> 00:14:23,430
please.

281
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:37,610
Have you taken a bath
with cold water recently?

282
00:14:37,610 --> 00:14:38,760
I came back late

283
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:41,860
on the night of the Autumn Festival.

284
00:14:41,970 --> 00:14:43,830
I had no time to wait for hot water,

285
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:45,520
so I used well water.

286
00:14:48,090 --> 00:14:49,820
That prescription is correct.

287
00:14:49,850 --> 00:14:51,890
It's just that your long, tiring journey

288
00:14:51,890 --> 00:14:53,160
and constant worries

289
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,970
have taken a toll on your illness.

290
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:55,640
After all,

291
00:14:58,010 --> 00:14:59,560
I've failed the Yue family

292
00:15:01,250 --> 00:15:02,330
and Rou.

293
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,530
I can't feel at ease.

294
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,680
Is it the famous Chengying Sword?

295
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,380
Sharp eyes, Your Highness.

296
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,730
Can I take it off to have a closer look?

297
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:15,400
Hold on.

298
00:15:21,850 --> 00:15:22,640
This sword

299
00:15:23,210 --> 00:15:24,610
was given by Duke of Song.

300
00:15:24,850 --> 00:15:26,450
It's as important as my life.

301
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,250
I never dare to play with it.

302
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:30,660
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

303
00:15:32,130 --> 00:15:33,730
A man of taste appreciates swords.

304
00:15:33,730 --> 00:15:35,040
I won't blame you for it.

305
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,520
Thank you for your magnanimity,
Your Highness.

306
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:39,180
You're indeed our role model.

307
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,890
Vice Commandant Wei,

308
00:15:42,890 --> 00:15:45,490
you can change it to a charcoal basin
to warm the room up.

309
00:15:45,490 --> 00:15:46,800
The high stove is producing

310
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:47,890
excessive scorching heat,

311
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:49,490
not good for your recovery.

312
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:51,020
I always feel freezing cold

313
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:52,490
at night.

314
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:54,210
I will just

315
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,910
reduce charcoal during the day.

316
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,300
That works too.

317
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,850
You don't need to change the prescription.

318
00:15:59,850 --> 00:16:02,050
A few days of rest will help you recover.

319
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,010
Thank you, Miss Qin.

320
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,280
Thank you, Your Highness.

321
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,890
Get some rest, Vice Commandant Wei.

322
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:09,560
Take care.

323
00:16:17,610 --> 00:16:19,160
Wei Yanzhi had a stove
burning in his room,

324
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:20,250
but the window was open

325
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:21,640
with super strong incense.

326
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,810
There must be something off.

327
00:16:22,810 --> 00:16:25,130
Chengying Sword is famous and priceless.

328
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:26,560
Why would Duke of Song
highly value his nephew

329
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,690
born of a concubine?

330
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,610
The burning ashes
in the mansion are all here.

331
00:16:30,610 --> 00:16:31,860
It's not winter yet. Only a few

332
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:33,190
people are burning charcoal.

333
00:16:33,190 --> 00:16:35,720
So they are
basically from Wei Yanzhi's room.

334
00:16:52,130 --> 00:16:52,990
Little Wan'er,

335
00:16:53,800 --> 00:16:55,680
what are you and Chi looking for?

336
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,250
It's so dirty.

337
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:58,560
Let the servants do it.

338
00:16:58,560 --> 00:16:59,890
They can't understand.

339
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:03,550
Do you have to search them all?

340
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,090
Master,

341
00:17:07,130 --> 00:17:09,590
Wei Qizhi has been arrested
and imprisoned.

342
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,090
Did he confess his crime?

343
00:17:11,090 --> 00:17:11,740
Not yet.

344
00:17:11,850 --> 00:17:13,560
But Prefect Huo has tortured him.

345
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:15,130
Ning, keep a close eye on these ashes.

346
00:17:15,130 --> 00:17:15,760
Let no one touch them.

347
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:16,040
Okay.

348
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,090
Let's go to the prefect's office.

349
00:17:17,090 --> 00:17:17,680
Let's go.

350
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:25,050
Your Highness,

351
00:17:25,050 --> 00:17:25,940
Miss Qin.

352
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,640
Wei Qizhi only confessed that

353
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:31,060
he sent the servant, Wu Shu,
to steal the postmortem report.

354
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:33,130
He refused to admit anything else.

355
00:17:33,329 --> 00:17:35,599
They are really stubborn.

356
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,770
Even torture couldn't make them
spit out the truth.

357
00:17:37,770 --> 00:17:38,609
Without evidence,

358
00:17:38,609 --> 00:17:40,369
how could you torture them, Prefect Huo?

359
00:17:40,369 --> 00:17:42,970
Besides, I haven't checked
his leg injury yet.

360
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:43,720
Where is he?

361
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,960
Your Highness,
the prison is foul and filthy.

362
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:46,920
Please...

363
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:49,320
I'll punish you for the arbitrary torture.

364
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:57,910
Prefect Huo, I'm impressed by your way

365
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:00,170
of interrogation and torture.

366
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,640
Were you trying to force him
to confess by torture?

367
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,370
He said his leg had been broken.

368
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,800
Of course, we should

369
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,000
go for the fatal spot.

370
00:18:09,050 --> 00:18:11,160
So I hit his injured part.

371
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:12,290
But he

372
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:13,960
refused to confess.

373
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,130
You broke his injured leg again.

374
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:15,880
Now we can't tell

375
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,610
whether he was limping before.

376
00:18:18,050 --> 00:18:19,440
Besides, the leg injury is hard to heal.

377
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,850
If he is disabled because of this

378
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:22,380
and proven innocent later,

379
00:18:22,850 --> 00:18:24,380
how can you make it up to him?

380
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:26,480
If he had no evil intentions,

381
00:18:26,530 --> 00:18:29,570
why would he
follow Song Rou all the way to Jingzhou?

382
00:18:29,570 --> 00:18:30,370
On the wedding day,

383
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:31,640
he lingered at the Shili Temple.

384
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:33,090
He stayed there one more day

385
00:18:33,090 --> 00:18:35,400
definitely to remove the traces of murder.

386
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,570
Sir, I'm innocent!

387
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:37,290
Sir!

388
00:18:38,130 --> 00:18:38,480
Sir!

389
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,050
Take him away.

390
00:18:39,050 --> 00:18:39,850
Let him speak.

391
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:42,400
Sir, my Young Master

392
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,570
was afraid that Miss Song's secret
would be exposed,

393
00:18:44,570 --> 00:18:45,920
causing her to be abused
by the Yue family,

394
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,640
so he came here despite his injured leg.

395
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,570
When we arrived in Jingzhou,

396
00:18:48,570 --> 00:18:50,400
we heard about Miss Song's death.

397
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:52,090
So he ordered me to steal
the postmortem report

398
00:18:52,090 --> 00:18:53,000
to figure out

399
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:55,210
how exactly Miss Song died.

400
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:58,240
My Young Master and Miss Song
didn't have an affair!

401
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,810
In no case would he murder her!

402
00:18:59,810 --> 00:19:01,570
Sirs! We're innocent!

403
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,960
Stop talking nonsense!

404
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:06,160
Wei Qizhi admitted that
he had an affair with Song Rou.

405
00:19:07,330 --> 00:19:09,850
Young Master Qizhi cherished Miss Song
as his own sister.

406
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,240
There's no way they had an affair!

407
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:12,680
No way he killed her!

408
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,880
Does Wei Qizhi write with his left hand?

409
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,890
Yes, so what?

410
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:17,440
Many people can write
with their left hands,

411
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,960
like our Second Young Master!

412
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,920
Why can Wei Yanzhi
use his left hand to write?

413
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,610
Young Master Qizhi was plagued by rashes
when he was little.

414
00:19:22,610 --> 00:19:24,440
Madam Wei was worried that
being left-handed jinxed it.

415
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:26,610
So she forced him
to write with his right hand.

416
00:19:26,610 --> 00:19:28,000
But he was so stubborn

417
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,110
that he refused to change.

418
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:31,530
To prevent Master Wei from favoring
the concubine's son because of it,

419
00:19:31,530 --> 00:19:32,960
she forced Second Young Master to write

420
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:34,200
with his left hand to destroy him.

421
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,680
But Young Master Qizhi didn't want

422
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,890
Young Master Yanzhi to be implicated,

423
00:19:36,890 --> 00:19:38,330
so he changed to use his right hand.

424
00:19:38,330 --> 00:19:39,590
So Second Young Master

425
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,130
ended up with better left-handed writing

426
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:42,680
than Young Master Qizhi.

427
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:44,980
Since when did Wei Qizhi
start to use porcelain only?

428
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:47,360
It's not that Young Master Qizhi
likes porcelain items only.

429
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:49,610
He's just disliked the scent of lacquer
since childhood.

430
00:19:49,610 --> 00:19:50,720
Other types of utensils

431
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,200
almost all contain lacquer more or less.

432
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,330
So he uses white-porcelain items
for convenience.

433
00:19:54,330 --> 00:19:55,660
I swear with my life that

434
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,980
Young Master Qizhi

435
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,810
is innocent!

436
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:01,920
Prefect Huo,

437
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:04,520
please get a physician
for Wei Qizhi right now.

438
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,610
I'll be on my way.

439
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,880
I didn't kill Rou.

440
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:10,130
It wasn't me.

441
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:12,810
I didn't kill her.

442
00:20:14,460 --> 00:20:15,330
I didn't.

443
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,170
Stop searching.

444
00:20:35,610 --> 00:20:36,810
I can arrest him first

445
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:38,640
and interrogate him in turn.

446
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:40,000
When he's exhausted,

447
00:20:40,220 --> 00:20:41,920
I'm sure he'll give himself away.

448
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,580
But we need sufficient evidence
to convict him.

449
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,850
The testimony can only serve as one of it.

450
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:48,310
It's not enough to confirm

451
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,980
that person as the murderer.

452
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,920
But this slow investigation might

453
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:53,440
give the real murderer a chance to escape.

454
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:55,440
Then our efforts will all be in vain.

455
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:58,480
It's easy for you
to convict someone, Your Highness,

456
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,770
but a wrong conviction
will ruin a man's entire life.

457
00:21:00,770 --> 00:21:02,330
Don't let impatience

458
00:21:02,330 --> 00:21:04,130
wreck the fairness of the laws.

459
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,770
Is this also the saying

460
00:21:09,770 --> 00:21:11,700
of Minister Shen Yi who you admire?

461
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:13,730
Yes.

462
00:21:17,050 --> 00:21:18,650
Thank you for your guidance.

463
00:21:19,130 --> 00:21:21,200
Miss Qin, please continue
to gather the evidence.

464
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,850
Leave the arrest work to me.

465
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:25,550
Thank you, Your Highness.

466
00:21:26,290 --> 00:21:28,650
But I want to ask you for one more favor.

467
00:21:30,550 --> 00:21:32,500
[Jingzhou Prefecture Office]

468
00:21:44,770 --> 00:21:45,770
Wei Qizhi,

469
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,280
since your leg is badly injured,

470
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,000
you can sit down and talk.

471
00:21:50,610 --> 00:21:52,470
Thank you for your kindness, sir.

472
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:54,090
I can stand.

473
00:22:02,570 --> 00:22:03,680
Wei Qizhi,

474
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:05,200
tell me

475
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,000
how you

476
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,000
got your leg hurt.

477
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:10,350
Two months ago, in the capital,

478
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:11,930
Duke of Song broke my leg.

479
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,890
And yesterday, you...

480
00:22:16,130 --> 00:22:16,990
That's enough.

481
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:19,240
I'm asking you why Duke of Song

482
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:23,340
beat you so hard that time.

483
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:25,290
Because I admitted

484
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,210
my affair

485
00:22:27,540 --> 00:22:29,130
with Miss Song.

486
00:22:29,850 --> 00:22:32,290
So is it true that
you had an affair with her?

487
00:22:33,570 --> 00:22:34,240
No.

488
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,240
Then why did you admit it?

489
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:39,750
Out with it!

490
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:46,290
Rou's reputation outweighed my life.

491
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,000
She said it was me.

492
00:22:49,210 --> 00:22:50,250
Then I'd admit it.

493
00:22:50,930 --> 00:22:51,740
Wei Qizhi,

494
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:53,570
it's very likely that

495
00:22:53,570 --> 00:22:55,530
Song Rou was killed by the one she loved.

496
00:22:55,530 --> 00:22:56,620
Can you really bear

497
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,000
to see the murderer get away with it?

498
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:03,000
That day, Rou came to me, crying

499
00:23:04,370 --> 00:23:06,640
and saying that
she had an affair with someone.

500
00:23:06,640 --> 00:23:08,240
After Duke of Song found out,

501
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:13,200
she blurted out my name out of panic.

502
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:14,850
Rou, tell me.

503
00:23:14,850 --> 00:23:16,440
I asked her who that man was,

504
00:23:17,090 --> 00:23:19,290
but she cried without saying anything.

505
00:23:19,370 --> 00:23:20,230
In the end,

506
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:23,000
she even forced me to claim
to be her lover by hurting herself.

507
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,960
Who on earth is he?

508
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:26,810
I can't say it!

509
00:23:26,890 --> 00:23:28,010
If others find out,

510
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,490
his future will be ruined.

511
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,320
I really love him.

512
00:23:34,260 --> 00:23:35,300
A few days later,

513
00:23:35,810 --> 00:23:37,440
Duke of Song showed up with his men,

514
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:40,440
breaking my leg
without giving me a chance to explain.

515
00:23:40,640 --> 00:23:43,240
In view of my previous grudge
against Duke of Song

516
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,840
and my promise to Rou
to pretend to be her lover,

517
00:23:45,850 --> 00:23:47,310
I admitted it out of anger.

518
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,930
Later, I was recuperating at home.

519
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:52,620
Yanzhi said that
Duke of Song didn't punish Rou.

520
00:23:52,810 --> 00:23:55,340
So I didn't rush to ask her
for the whole story.

521
00:23:56,050 --> 00:23:58,310
Until she left the capital for marriage,

522
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:00,990
the person she was protecting
still hadn't shown up.

523
00:24:00,990 --> 00:24:02,100
What a coward.

524
00:24:02,130 --> 00:24:02,840
How is it?

525
00:24:02,870 --> 00:24:03,670
Young Master,

526
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,990
Miss Song was murdered.

527
00:24:08,170 --> 00:24:09,980
She even got beheaded.

528
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:15,440
I was afraid that person would betray her.

529
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,950
If the Yue family finds out

530
00:24:17,090 --> 00:24:18,130
about her infidelity,

531
00:24:18,130 --> 00:24:19,930
she wouldn't be able to survive.

532
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:22,240
So I followed her here secretly

533
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,810
to confirm her safety.

534
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,850
I didn't expect to hear this bad news.

535
00:24:28,890 --> 00:24:29,720
What the hell are you doing?

536
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,290
Guards!

537
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,200
Hold him down.

538
00:24:59,610 --> 00:25:01,240
Wei Qizhi suffers from a rare disease.

539
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,780
His contact with the lacquerware
will lead to rashes.

540
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:06,090
At worst,
wind evil can infiltrate his organs,

541
00:25:06,090 --> 00:25:07,090
knocking him out.

542
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:10,960
So it's rumored in the capital that
he only uses white-porcelain items.

543
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,890
That's the reason.

544
00:25:11,890 --> 00:25:13,890
Judging from his symptoms just now,

545
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,530
he'd never use the dusted-gold paper

546
00:25:15,530 --> 00:25:17,240
that contains golden lacquer.

547
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:17,640
Yes.

548
00:25:18,330 --> 00:25:20,090
So the victim swallowed
the dusted-gold paper

549
00:25:20,090 --> 00:25:22,290
to protect someone else instead of him.

550
00:25:22,610 --> 00:25:23,530
So,

551
00:25:24,090 --> 00:25:27,000
he's not Miss Song's lover?

552
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:28,000
Yes.

553
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:29,950
Now I know who the murderer is.

554
00:25:30,770 --> 00:25:32,290
Bet you do too, Miss Qin.

555
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:34,480
Your Highness, just do it.

556
00:25:34,810 --> 00:25:36,360
I will get the real culprit

557
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:38,220
with solid evidence.

558
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,400
Vice Commandant Wei,

559
00:26:20,650 --> 00:26:22,580
where are you going in such a hurry?

560
00:26:25,240 --> 00:26:27,100
Take it out and get what's inside.

561
00:26:27,240 --> 00:26:27,610
Yes.

562
00:26:27,610 --> 00:26:29,810
Your eldest brother has been arrested.

563
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,090
If you are innocent,

564
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:32,530
why are you trying to run away?

565
00:26:32,530 --> 00:26:33,730
I'm not running away.

566
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:38,000
I just want to go back to the capital
and report this to the elders.

567
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:38,640
What?

568
00:26:38,930 --> 00:26:41,730
Are you going to lock me up
in this mansion forever?

569
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:50,240
Still can't let me touch it?

570
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:52,610
A man of dignity can be killed,
but not humiliated.

571
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:54,160
Chengying means a lot to me.

572
00:26:54,190 --> 00:26:55,640
No one can touch it.

573
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:58,690
Did you hear that, Prefect Huo?

574
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:01,090
Vice Commandant Wei said it himself that

575
00:27:01,090 --> 00:27:02,290
even I

576
00:27:02,290 --> 00:27:04,400
couldn't touch his Chengying Sword.

577
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:07,160
Yes, I heard it clearly.

578
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,530
Good.

579
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,050
Bring it in!

580
00:27:24,050 --> 00:27:24,920
Wei Yanzhi,

581
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,570
do you know what this is?

582
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,480
This is the glue left by the burnt fat.

583
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,370
Although you broke the skull,

584
00:27:31,370 --> 00:27:32,300
lit the incense,

585
00:27:32,370 --> 00:27:33,810
and opened the window to ventilate,

586
00:27:33,810 --> 00:27:35,740
you forgot to clean the iron tongs.

587
00:27:35,770 --> 00:27:38,700
Silver-frost charcoal
wouldn't leave such a stain.

588
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:42,050
Take the evidence away.

589
00:27:42,130 --> 00:27:42,690
Yes.

590
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:48,720
Found it, Your Highness.

591
00:27:49,610 --> 00:27:50,670
Give it to Miss Qin.

592
00:28:41,890 --> 00:28:43,420
He really killed Miss Song.

593
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:46,000
According to the traces on the skull,

594
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,720
the murderer must have stabbed the sword

595
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:50,680
directly into the victim's occipital bone
from behind

596
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:53,020
and cut off her head
to hide the sword mark.

597
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,770
Wei Yanzhi,

598
00:28:56,330 --> 00:28:57,990
the evidence is irrefutable.

599
00:28:58,090 --> 00:28:59,890
Do you have anything else to say?

600
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,850
The murderer dipped the victim's blood,

601
00:29:12,850 --> 00:29:15,440
disguised the wedding sedan
as the crime scene,

602
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:17,850
dressed the victim up in the wedding gown,

603
00:29:17,850 --> 00:29:19,180
and put her in the sedan.

604
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:23,390
To stop Miss Qin from examining the body,

605
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:26,330
you played the headless female corpse
to scare her.

606
00:29:26,330 --> 00:29:28,480
You also tried to use
the ink on the wedding gown

607
00:29:28,480 --> 00:29:31,010
to frame your legitimate brother,
Wei Qizhi.

608
00:29:35,050 --> 00:29:36,660
To pin the crime on Wei Qizhi

609
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:38,590
and get rid of me, the examiner,

610
00:29:38,810 --> 00:29:40,770
you sent your loyal Captain of the Guard,
Wei Cheng,

611
00:29:40,770 --> 00:29:42,170
to impersonate Wei Qizhi

612
00:29:42,330 --> 00:29:44,530
and assassinate me at the lantern fair.

613
00:29:57,190 --> 00:29:59,160
When you found that
the assassination failed,

614
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,960
and the autopsy was inevitable,

615
00:30:01,810 --> 00:30:04,240
you ordered Wei Cheng
to burn the morgue overnight

616
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,480
and attempted to destroy
the evidence once again.

617
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,810
Also, you heated up the stove

618
00:30:07,810 --> 00:30:09,370
to burn the victim's head.

619
00:30:10,130 --> 00:30:10,900
Now,

620
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,860
we have the witness and evidence.

621
00:30:13,130 --> 00:30:15,050
You murdered the victim,

622
00:30:15,610 --> 00:30:16,610
Wei Yanzhi.

623
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:22,320
How ruthless and insane.

624
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,840
We've got solid evidence.

625
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,370
What else do you have to say?

626
00:30:30,530 --> 00:30:32,290
Me? Ruthless and insane?

627
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,720
That woman

628
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:35,130
was insane!

629
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:39,720
She had such a great marriage

630
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:41,450
with a member of the Yue family,

631
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,770
but why did she pester me

632
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,500
and force me to elope with her?

633
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:46,460
Why?

634
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:49,950
My elder brother
is the legitimate young master!

635
00:30:50,370 --> 00:30:52,500
They broke his leg like it was nothing.

636
00:30:52,890 --> 00:30:54,170
What if it were me?

637
00:30:55,370 --> 00:30:57,100
I would have been dead, I guess.

638
00:30:57,570 --> 00:30:58,480
Sha had no idea

639
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:01,800
about the consequences
of going against the Duke!

640
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,000
Yanzhi.

641
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:09,700
You're finally here
to take me away with you.

642
00:31:11,850 --> 00:31:13,890
Why did you come out
in your wedding dress?

643
00:31:13,890 --> 00:31:15,290
If someone witnesses it,

644
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,120
you and I will be done for.

645
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,130
I was anxious to meet you.

646
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,690
Don't worry.

647
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,400
I've sent the Nanny away.

648
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:23,960
She won't notice.

649
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,580
Do you have my letter

650
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,160
with you?

651
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,610
I was afraid that the Nanny might see it,

652
00:31:30,610 --> 00:31:32,140
so I swallowed it secretly.

653
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,440
Oh, dear...

654
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,530
Why?

655
00:31:40,890 --> 00:31:44,020
It must've been a pain
to swallow the dusted-gold paper.

656
00:31:44,130 --> 00:31:44,860
For you,

657
00:31:46,090 --> 00:31:47,550
I'm not afraid of any pain.

658
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:49,580
Yanzhi,

659
00:31:49,810 --> 00:31:51,290
take me away tonight.

660
00:31:51,810 --> 00:31:53,960
I'd rather die

661
00:31:54,530 --> 00:31:56,130
than let other men touch me.

662
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,050
I won't marry

663
00:31:58,680 --> 00:32:00,810
anyone other than you in my life.

664
00:32:01,890 --> 00:32:02,850
Can we

665
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:06,640
be together forever?

666
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,500
Don't think like that.

667
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:13,530
I'll feel bad.

668
00:32:15,850 --> 00:32:17,090
Let's leave tonight.

669
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,260
We'll go far, far away.

670
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,460
Our destination is

671
00:32:20,770 --> 00:32:22,100
wherever you want to go.

672
00:32:24,570 --> 00:32:25,770
If you say yes,

673
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:30,640
I'll cherish you, love you,
and be with you

674
00:32:31,290 --> 00:32:32,290
forever and ever.

675
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:35,620
Nothing will separate us.

676
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,200
There will be neither
the legitimate young lady of Song family

677
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,530
nor the young master's wife of Yue family.

678
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:20,720
I will only be Mrs. Wei, plainly dressed.

679
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,970
I would go anywhere with you

680
00:33:24,060 --> 00:33:25,530
as a loving couple

681
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,530
forever.

682
00:33:47,850 --> 00:33:48,680
But...

683
00:33:52,390 --> 00:33:53,910
I don't want that.

684
00:34:09,370 --> 00:34:11,370
She gave up
the wealthy and luxurious life for you,

685
00:34:11,370 --> 00:34:13,770
yet you killed her
for your selfish desire.

686
00:34:13,890 --> 00:34:16,400
How dare you say
she didn't care about your feelings?

687
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,890
As a concubine's son,
I've been through trials and tribulations,

688
00:34:18,890 --> 00:34:20,220
including those caused

689
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:22,740
by my legitimate mother, to come this far.

690
00:34:22,740 --> 00:34:24,850
Why should I give up my future and live

691
00:34:24,850 --> 00:34:26,330
a low-profile life for her?

692
00:34:26,330 --> 00:34:27,600
Why should I?

693
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:39,670
This foolish and hateful woman

694
00:34:39,889 --> 00:34:42,040
tried to ruin my life with love.

695
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:46,120
She deserved to die.

696
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,310
The woman you said is called Song Rou.

697
00:34:55,310 --> 00:34:56,920
The most foolish thing she did

698
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:58,040
was to use all her intelligence

699
00:34:58,040 --> 00:34:59,290
to protect you!

700
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:00,650
If she didn't swallow
that paper

701
00:35:00,650 --> 00:35:02,480
you used to lure her
into your deadly trap,

702
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:04,690
you'd have
been brought to justice long ago!

703
00:35:04,690 --> 00:35:06,960
You cruelly hurt the woman
who loved you deeply.

704
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,280
You're the one who deserves to die!

705
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:09,250
So what?

706
00:35:10,330 --> 00:35:11,790
As long as I don't love her,

707
00:35:17,250 --> 00:35:19,690
even if she died
ten thousand times for me,

708
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,960
it'd only be a mistake.

709
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:28,480
A mistake!

710
00:35:45,290 --> 00:35:47,040
If Miss Song knows

711
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,290
someone still cares about her,

712
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,810
she'll rest in peace.

713
00:35:52,730 --> 00:35:53,690
Without you,

714
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:57,540
the person who cares about her
wouldn't have survived.

715
00:36:05,850 --> 00:36:06,540
Xu He.

716
00:36:08,210 --> 00:36:09,400
Since the case is closed,

717
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,120
now

718
00:36:10,250 --> 00:36:12,650
let's repair Miss Song's body.

719
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:13,800
Miss Qin,

720
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:15,170
I don't understand.

721
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:16,600
The case is closed.

722
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:18,080
What's the point of repairing her body?

723
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:19,170
Normally, we'd return

724
00:36:19,170 --> 00:36:20,850
the body to his or her family.

725
00:36:20,850 --> 00:36:21,650
If no one takes the body,

726
00:36:21,650 --> 00:36:22,690
we'd buy a coffin

727
00:36:22,850 --> 00:36:24,520
and bury the body at the back mountain.

728
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:27,850
We had to choose the autopsy
to prove someone's innocence.

729
00:36:30,290 --> 00:36:31,880
The victim's corpse

730
00:36:32,290 --> 00:36:33,730
revealed the truth to us.

731
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:36,400
We should restore her dignity.

732
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:42,170
Miss Qin,

733
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,330
why did you start to call her

734
00:36:46,730 --> 00:36:48,130
Miss Song again just now?

735
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,200
Because from today onwards,

736
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:52,840
I don't need to see her
as evidence anymore.

737
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,690
I can finally send Miss Song off

738
00:36:54,890 --> 00:36:56,770
without feeling bad.

