♪ Here I meet you, gentleman ♪

746
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:57,230
♪ In absolute relief ♪

747
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:54,460
♪ Gloomy wind and rain ♪

748
00:38:54,490 --> 00:38:58,470
♪ Ever-lasting crowing ♪

749
00:38:58,490 --> 00:39:02,380
♪ Here I meet you, gentleman ♪

750
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:05,960
♪ In pure delight ♪

751
00:39:06,740 --> 00:39:12,720
♪ Endless wind and rain ♪

752
00:39:14,650 --> 00:39:20,720
♪ What a pity ♪

753
00:39:22,670 --> 00:39:29,210
♪ Endless wind and rain ♪

754
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:37,480
♪ What a pity ♪

755
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:36,690
Thank you.

756
00:39:53,330 --> 00:39:54,600
You have only half an hour.

757
00:39:54,600 --> 00:39:55,400
Don't forget.

758
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:56,690
Yes.

759
00:40:12,970 --> 00:40:14,300
What are you doing here?

760
00:40:16,250 --> 00:40:18,210
To laugh at me for your mother?

761
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:20,040
Yanzhi,

762
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,200
I just want to ask you.

763
00:40:23,250 --> 00:40:25,000
Rou loved you deeply

764
00:40:25,650 --> 00:40:27,510
and was pregnant with your child.

765
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,400
Have you ever had
any real feelings for her?

766
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:34,520
You want to scold me for her?

767
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:38,330
Even now, you still feel no remorse?

768
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,370
Who are you to scold me?

769
00:40:44,890 --> 00:40:46,690
Because I'm your elder brother!

770
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,660
I don't have an elder brother.

771
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:53,170
As the Wei family's
legitimate young master,

772
00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:54,960
you were born with all the honor

773
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,350
and everyone's love.

774
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,520
What about me?

775
00:40:58,290 --> 00:40:59,850
I'm just a concubine's lowly son

776
00:40:59,850 --> 00:41:02,780
who couldn't even see
his own mother before she died.

777
00:41:03,170 --> 00:41:05,900
Your mother made my mother
die a miserable death.

778
00:41:06,080 --> 00:41:07,760
Do you think I don't remember?

779
00:41:09,080 --> 00:41:10,060
All these years,

780
00:41:10,210 --> 00:41:12,230
when your mother disciplined you,

781
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:14,920
I'd suffer double the punishment with you.

782
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,960
I couldn't join the Patrol Battalion

783
00:41:16,960 --> 00:41:18,770
due to your dislike for Duke of Song.

784
00:41:18,770 --> 00:41:21,170
I was the one
who liked learning the zither,

785
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:23,370
but your mother
only allowed you to learn it.

786
00:41:23,370 --> 00:41:24,330
Were it not for this,

787
00:41:24,330 --> 00:41:26,250
I wouldn't have
turned to Rou to learn the zither,

788
00:41:26,250 --> 00:41:28,710
and things
wouldn't have ended up like this!

789
00:41:32,270 --> 00:41:34,930
So you've been holding
deep grudges against me.

790
00:41:37,290 --> 00:41:38,850
I'm sorry.

791
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:46,590
No more hypocritical look of grief.

792
00:41:48,810 --> 00:41:51,810
After all these years
of the game of fake brotherhood,

793
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,480
I've had enough.

794
00:42:00,250 --> 00:42:01,080
Now, leave.

795
00:42:03,690 --> 00:42:05,090
No matter what you think,

796
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,170
I have never tried to hurt you.

797
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,770
After we part today,

798
00:42:23,770 --> 00:42:25,250
I hope you can

799
00:42:26,890 --> 00:42:28,490
find peace in your next life.

800
00:43:09,860 --> 00:43:12,110
[Here rests Miss Song,
Duke of Song's legitimate daughter]

801
00:43:12,470 --> 00:43:14,220
Poor Miss Song.

802
00:43:14,650 --> 00:43:17,250
Were it not for Grand Princess
and Young Master Wei Qizhi,

803
00:43:17,250 --> 00:43:19,380
she wouldn't have had a proper burial.

804
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:22,730
Young Master Wei Qizhi
insisted on burying her in Jingzhou.

805
00:43:22,730 --> 00:43:23,420
Seems like

806
00:43:23,810 --> 00:43:26,610
he's completely disappointed
in the Song family.

807
00:43:27,210 --> 00:43:29,270
Maybe because he knows them too well,

808
00:43:29,370 --> 00:43:31,000
he chose to do it this way.

809
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:33,800
Given Duke of Song's character,

810
00:43:33,920 --> 00:43:35,350
he wouldn't let Miss Song

811
00:43:35,890 --> 00:43:37,890
be buried in their family cemetery.

812
00:43:38,690 --> 00:43:40,040
It'd be better to bury her here.

813
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:41,370
It's a beautiful place,

814
00:43:41,770 --> 00:43:43,770
guaranteeing a peaceful next life.

815
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:47,020
Whenever I think about it,
I feel terrified.

816
00:43:47,400 --> 00:43:48,400
A woman

817
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:49,580
got killed

818
00:43:49,890 --> 00:43:51,370
due to her infatuation.

819
00:43:52,120 --> 00:43:54,890
In order to protect
the family reputation, her father

820
00:43:54,890 --> 00:43:56,820
just left her body alone like this!

821
00:43:57,520 --> 00:43:59,850
She couldn't even return to her hometown.

822
00:44:00,120 --> 00:44:01,080
Are these men

823
00:44:01,080 --> 00:44:02,210
heartless?

824
00:44:02,960 --> 00:44:04,760
It has nothing to do with gender.

825
00:44:04,890 --> 00:44:07,210
Be it Duke of Song or Wei Yanzhi,

826
00:44:07,650 --> 00:44:09,080
they are selfish people

827
00:44:09,080 --> 00:44:10,770
who care about themselves only.

828
00:44:10,770 --> 00:44:12,710
Seems like as women,

829
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:15,600
we'd better stay single
to protect ourselves.

830
00:44:17,670 --> 00:44:19,710
Master, the case is closed.

831
00:44:20,040 --> 00:44:21,520
Should we go back to the capital now?

832
00:44:21,520 --> 00:44:22,120
Bai Feng,

833
00:44:23,370 --> 00:44:25,100
I think I've made some progress

834
00:44:25,170 --> 00:44:27,030
on the case we're investigating.

835
00:44:27,330 --> 00:44:29,560
You mean new clues
about Prince Jin's case?

836
00:44:29,560 --> 00:44:30,250
Nope.

837
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:33,040
But we got a more powerful sidekick

838
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:35,460
to investigate this case.

839
00:44:37,170 --> 00:44:38,490
Send a message to the capital

840
00:44:38,490 --> 00:44:40,820
to suspend my entry
to the Ministry of War.

841
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:43,830
I want to be transferred
to the Ministry of Justice.

